{"id":9916,"date":"2022-03-10T14:18:55","date_gmt":"2022-03-10T08:48:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=9916"},"modified":"2022-03-10T14:18:55","modified_gmt":"2022-03-10T08:48:55","slug":"augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html","title":{"rendered":"Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Apps- Everything You Want To Know"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9918\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ar-based-remote-assistance-app.jpg\" alt=\"AR-based Remote Assistance App\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ar-based-remote-assistance-app.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ar-based-remote-assistance-app-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ar-based-remote-assistance-app-768x373.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The future of remote assistance solutions lies in augmented reality, meaning that specialists from across the globe can help you out with your technical issues and at the same time take care of your schedule by remotely attending meetings and conferences on your behalf. This article will introduce you to Augmented Reality Remote Assistance solutions so that you know exactly what they are, how they work, and why they are superior to traditional remote assistance methods.<\/p>\n<div class=\"list\">\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Table_of_contents\"><\/span>Table of contents<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#remote-assistance\">What is AR-based remote assistance?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#benefits\">What are the benefits of remote assistance solutions?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#challenges\">What are the challenges in AR remote assistance apps?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#solutions\">What are AR remote assistance solutions capable of?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#industries\">What types of industries are using remote assistance solutions?<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Is_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance\"><\/span><a id=\"remote-assistance\"><\/a>What Is Augmented Reality Remote Assistance?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Augmented reality (AR) is a live, direct or indirect, view of a physical, real-world environment whose elements are augmented by computer-generated sensory input such as sound, video, graphics, or GPS data. The input is merged with the physical world in real-time to create an augmented version of reality. An Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solution allows medical professionals and users alike to virtually interact through video conferencing software.<\/p>\n<p>AR Remote assistance has grown exponentially because it represents a valuable tool for businesses across various industries to stay ahead of competitors by enhancing their services, making processes more efficient, and allowing workers from other companies that utilize remote assistance tools themselves to stay informed about developments within their field which will result in even greater productivity for them without requiring major investments on either end. There is no limit to where AR can be used.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benefits_of_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance_Solutions\"><\/span><a id=\"benefits\"><\/a>Benefits of Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solutions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Augmented reality, which involves the real-time overlay of computer-generated imagery on top of the real world, has many applications in the modern business world. Remote assistance apps in particular are being widely adopted by modern enterprises to benefit operations, increase efficiency and even build trust with clients and partners. Here\u2019s how augmented reality remote assistance apps work and what they can do for your business.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Real-time_Support\"><\/span>Real-time Support<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Today\u2019s businesses are under a lot of pressure to be 24\/7. The expectation that your customer service department will always be available, at all hours of day or night, has only intensified over time\u2014and it won\u2019t be going away anytime soon. Of course, anyone in IT knows that real-time support can be difficult to provide, particularly when you\u2019re managing several remote locations and multiple teams.<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Improve_Service_Quality\"><\/span>Improve Service Quality<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In today\u2019s economy, businesses don\u2019t need to be physically present in a location to profit from it. Consider how ubiquitous drive-through restaurants are. They don\u2019t actually serve their food; customers still have to come inside and pay in order to eat it. But these restaurants create an interactive experience that leads consumers right where they want them: at their cash registers. The rise of augmented reality will have a similar effect, with remote assistance as one of its most promising applications.<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Efficiency_of_Workflow\"><\/span>Efficiency of Workflow<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>It makes it easier to identify problems and pinpoints their exact locations, keeps remote workers up-to-date with real-time information from your experts, allows them to receive step-by-step instructions, etc. The list of benefits goes on and on. And thanks to rapidly developing AR technology, no one will ever miss a single opportunity!<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Streamline_Business_Processes\"><\/span>Streamline Business Processes<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Though not as pervasive as many other augmented reality applications, remote assistance tools offer a number of benefits to both technicians and clients. For one, they are simple: many require little more than a user\u2019s smartphone and internet connection. They also streamline business processes: when you can easily see what your IT expert sees, it\u2019s easier to help them diagnose an issue.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_are_the_Challenges_in_AR_Remote_Assistance_Apps\"><\/span><a id=\"challenges\"><\/a>What are the Challenges in AR Remote Assistance Apps?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>What are some of these challenges? Well, in remote assistance apps, it is common for both parties to be speaking different languages, so there\u2019s no shared visual context between them. They may also have incompatible platforms or devices (e.g., iOS versus Android), which poses additional issues as well as complexities in how data is relayed and interpreted. Because Augmented Reality technology will likely become mainstream before remote-assistance applications do, there is an opportunity for communication companies to play a big role in shaping what Augmented Reality Remote Assistance technology looks like.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_are_AR_Remote_Assistance_Solutions_Capable_Of\"><\/span><a id=\"solutions\"><\/a>What are AR Remote Assistance Solutions Capable Of?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>One way that AR-based Remote Assistance App can be particularly beneficial is by helping users bridge language barriers. Using AR interfaces makes sense because they allow people who speak different languages to interact using their primary senses\u2014sight and hearing\u2014as opposed to typing on a keyboard and relying on text translation tools. In terms of potential uses, remote assistance apps could help with anything from simple tasks like changing a flat tire on your car all the way up to more complex tasks like changing an engine part on your HVAC system at home.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Different_Industries_are_Using_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance_Solutions\"><\/span><a id=\"industries\"><\/a>How Different Industries are Using Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solutions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>One of top ways different industries are using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/augmented-reality-application-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Augmented Reality Solutions<\/a> is in sales and marketing. This allows companies to digitally exhibit themselves in real-time at trade shows, conferences, and events. It also makes it easier for salespeople when trying to sell their products over distance, since they can quickly show potential clients what their product looks like before taking any orders or making any deliveries. Other uses for ARRA will likely emerge as more people use it and get creative with how they apply ARRA technology for both personal and professional purposes.<\/p>\n<p>Some examples include remote training, automobile assembly, navigation support, robot control. the list goes on! As <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.ng\/remote-assistance-solutions.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AR-based Remote Assistance App<\/a> becomes more accessible and commonplace, new ideas will crop up from all areas of industry as people figure out how best to utilize these advanced tools.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Conclusion\"><\/span>Conclusion<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Augmented reality remote assistance solutions help organizations provide them with a competitive advantage. Find out how you can also leverage AR for your business needs.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Table_of_contents\" title=\"Table of contents\">Table of contents<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#What_Is_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance\" title=\"What Is Augmented Reality Remote Assistance?\">What Is Augmented Reality Remote Assistance?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Benefits_of_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance_Solutions\" title=\"Benefits of Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solutions\">Benefits of Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solutions<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Real-time_Support\" title=\"Real-time Support\">Real-time Support<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Improve_Service_Quality\" title=\"Improve Service Quality\">Improve Service Quality<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Efficiency_of_Workflow\" title=\"Efficiency of Workflow\">Efficiency of Workflow<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#Streamline_Business_Processes\" title=\"Streamline Business Processes\">Streamline Business Processes<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#What_are_the_Challenges_in_AR_Remote_Assistance_Apps\" title=\"What are the Challenges in AR Remote Assistance Apps?\">What are the Challenges in AR Remote Assistance Apps?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#What_are_AR_Remote_Assistance_Solutions_Capable_Of\" title=\"What are AR Remote Assistance Solutions Capable Of?\">What are AR Remote Assistance Solutions Capable Of?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/augmented-reality-remote-assistance-apps-everything-you-want-to-know.html\/#How_Different_Industries_are_Using_Augmented_Reality_Remote_Assistance_Solutions\" title=\"How Different Industries are Using Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Solutions\">How Different Industries are Using Augmented Reality Remote Assistance Sol